                        Garfield Star Sleeper Logo


    Did you know that most kids need at least 9 hours of sleep every
    night!!? That's right, and Garfield  a Star Sleeper  has teamed up
    with the National Center on Sleep Disorders Research to tell you all
    about sleep and how getting enough sleep at night helps you do your
    best during the day. Sleep Well. Do Well.


